##10 Days in the city: The story of a Wuhan isolator

MICRO-SIGNAL CCTVNEWS center

Function introduction, the Central Radio and Television News Media Center public number, provides current political, social, financial and economic, sports, Sudden News, as well as weather, road conditions, live video broadcast and other service information.

As of February 1, Xiao An, a post-90s legal worker from Anhui Province, had spent 10 days in self-isolation in Wuhan by herself. During these 10 days, she recorded what she heard, saw and felt with words and pictures, her fear and love, her fear and courage, her frustration and hope.
Under the epidemic situation, the human's joys and sorrows and emotions began to be broken through, so, this article from the epidemic center of Wuhan "sealed city diary" , perhaps more or less can see your heart and mine.
This is CCTV news special planning "epidemic under the face of life, " the sixth article series.

January 23,2020
Day One

January 23,2020

Day One

Wake up, "closed city" , looking at the news, imperceptible, eyes a little acid.

Friends on Wechat urged me to store food, I realized the seriousness of the problem, teeth did not brush, face did not wash, put on a mask, glasses and gloves, rushed to the neighborhood supermarket.
Sure enough, the neighborhood mini-mart was empty, and the fresh produce store was closed for the New Year.
The neighborhood supermarket is empty
I have a little Meng, busy take out a mobile phone to start Baidu near the big supermarket, at that moment, the hand actually a little shake, "supermarket" two words have been spelled several times not right.

Nearby big supermarket has some distance, but the road is empty, no bus, no subway, can't see the shadow of the taxi, T3, Cao Cao, Didi... all are "nearby unusable vehicle" . My hand trembled even more, and at last I could not help crouching by the roadside and crying. Why is this happening? It was fine a few days ago? I didn't even go home. I stayed in Wuhan. Why is that?
Squatting for a while, my feet a bit sore, I ran in the empty roadside. At that time, too late sad, just want to hurry to the supermarket, store food!
The new big supermarket is a little bit off-center, but it's super crowded! Shelves are constantly being bought out and restocked. There was no confusion, everything was in order, although very crowded, but behind the mask, is a calm face.
The checkout line was long, and dad in the back coughed a few times, and everyone backed away alertly. Dad Wore a mask, but his voice was still loud: "Don't be afraid, don't be afraid, I smoke all the year round. " Even so, everyone kept their distance by mutual agreement.
In the big supermarket, people line up in an orderly manner to check out
When I came out of the supermarket, the lady at the cash register was so kind as to help me pack the eggs, and told me over and over again not to crush them; the mother-in-law next to me opened the door for me, seeing that I had both bags in my hands. Things are heavy, the way home is long, but the heart is still warm.

Passing the neighborhood supermarket, pleased to see the clerk in the replenishment, fresh vegetables have been in place, the shop manager shouted at the door: "We do not rest, tomorrow also open, to ensure supply. "
The winter in Wuhan is very cold this year, but at this time I still feel very warm. Bad News comes in from time to time, but I believe, my God, that it will come to light.
My city is sick. My city is healthy.

January 24,2020
The next day,

January 24,2020

The next day,

Last night waiting for Hubei data until 2:00 a.m. , every day to brush data, it seems to be the only thing I can do.

When I woke up, it was only 7 am, I opened my phone, I saw the numbers going up, I felt sick in my heart, I forced myself to sleep again, I tossed and turned until after 9 am, I got up and felt my forehead as if everything was OK, I felt my temperature, 36.4, a Long Sigh of relief.
All Day, I didn't know what to do. When I used to go to work, I just wanted to sleep in, brush up on the TV, or cook something delicious at home. Now I have a lot of time, but I don't know what to do. Force oneself not to see micro-blog, not to see all about the epidemic, but always can not help but to brush, and then panic, sad, tangled.
The afternoon temperature was not very stable, accidentally measured a 37.2, I panicked, repeatedly remeasured, began Random Thoughts: is it from the hospital tooth extraction? Did my cough daddy give it to me yesterday? What if I do have it? Call 120. Will a doctor pick me up? How do you get to the hospital without transportation? What will happen to my parents if I die..
Today is the New Year's Eve, my mother asked me to cook some delicious treats for myself. I didn't do anything, what to reward, but the word on the tip of my tongue, became "sure ah, a person's New Year's Eve dinner, also want rich and delicate. ".
New Year's Eve dinner for one: Ravioli with instant noodles
Not In the mood to see the Spring Festival gala, but that ad hoc reading made me cry again, I really feel sorry for those who are fighting in the front line, too much touched, beyond words.
It's new year, and I hear firecrackers! Firecracker can drive away"Xi"this monster, should also be able to drive away these viruses.
Wuhan, wake up. I'm still here. We're all here.

January 25,2020
Day Three

January 25,2020

Day Three

I woke up in a daze, and the next day, thankfully, I was alive and well.
Open micro-blog, see many friends of the message, feel warm. There are some not so friendly words, said I was creating panic, even said "Wuhan deserved" and so on. It's cold and it's sad. As a person who was not born in Wuhan, but has lived in Wuhan for many years, I would like to say a few words on behalf of Wuhan.
This time the virus is related to eating game, but most of us in Wuhan do not eat game. That day, a foreign friend sent me a wechat message saying "you should stop drinking bat soup" , I almost spit it out... looking at the devastation of Wuhan, looking at the rising number of confirmed cases, we hate those who sell game and eat it more than anyone else.
I know, Wuhan this time to all parts of the country added trouble, because some people run around, infected others, here, to apologize to everyone. However, we, like you, did not know the seriousness of the matter until Zhong said the virus was contagious. Before that, we had seen "no obvious human-to-human transmission" .
We were all surprised when the news of the human-to-human transmission came out. That day, I squatted before the packed luggage, silently sent a long time to stay, two hours before the departure of the train returned the ticket. In the phone I told my mother I do not go back, my mother said "you are safe" , I heard the tears fell down. At that time, Wuhan has not "closed" , at that time, refund also fee, but, countless people and I, chose to stay behind, because we do not want to risk their own and other people's health.
I returned my ticket two hours before I left
See a lot of people online scold Wuhan people, said, "you see, before the city fled so many people, Wuhan people are really a scourge" , we really feel bad. Wuhan has a population of ten million people, and there are always some disobedient children who choose to flee because of fear, affection and ignorance.
Wuhan is also an important transportation hub, a tourist resort, to business, tourism, transfer have, suddenly saw the next day to "closed" , do not go nowhere to live, they chose to leave overnight. But Anyway, yes, Wuhan is a drag on everyone, and we're really sorry. Wuhan this child, no good, and so on the end of things, the mother of the motherland and other provinces and cities of children, must be good to criticize her.
Friend's mother is a doctor, hard for a whole year, asked for annual leave, want to rest at home. I got the call, and I went straight to the hospital.
A co-worker whose boyfriend is a cop said she was scared but proud.
A girl from far away, a doctor, very young, said they'd be on call 24 hours a day.
A conversation with a doctor friend

I heard that the People's Liberation Army uncle came (it should be the People's Liberation Army brothers and sisters) , did not feel how before, but this time, to hear the news, especially relieved. We're braver with them.
Today is the first day of the New Year, however, the New Year in Wuhan is still on its way, I believe, soon, it will be truly "a New Year" .

January 26,2020
Day Four

January 26,2020

Day Four

Feeling much better about myself today, I learned to put my phone down and do something more meaningful: pick up a guitar that had fallen on dust, and begin to chat with the opposite saxophone, as if it were a time of day, the Opposite Saxophone will ring, as if to tell the homesick, I do not know how many people in the crowded windows, and I, the ears are listening, the heart is playing.
Tell me something happy. The video of him shouting through the air amused many people. Indeed, this is our real life. A person play Mahjong four people, count melon seeds at home, share Dragon 18 palm nine Yin true movement map. ... More and more jokes on cell phones, laughter replacing fear. Thank you, everyone, for making this not-so-happy holiday so much fun.
Unexpectedly found that a few days ago, the Chinese cabbage stem, even germination! ! When I cut it off to throw it away, I suddenly remembered the little video in Weibo. I put it in a Plastic Cup, added some water and ignored it. It was forgotten in the corner, but it sprouted! !
Sprouted Stalk of cabbage

Spring, it seems, is here.
Spring is here. Will Victory Be far behind? !

January 27,2020
Day Five

January 27,2020

Day Five

2020, can you turn it off and reboot?
In the morning, two pieces of bad news: Kobe and his daughter, Gigi, were gone; another friend had a fever, a mild one, but a cough, weakness, and loss of appetite, as if each had been poisoned.
I'm scared, too, because I've been around her before. If she is infected, I also checked the Wuhan Medical Guidelines, which say that if confirmed, in-patient isolation treatment needs to prepare their own supplies. Thoughts, if I really have an accident, body weakness, which have the strength to prepare daily necessities, no one can help me clean up. So be prepared.
For oneself prepared a change of clothes, some basic daily necessities, packed a package of things, one by one to take out, repeatedly toss about for a long time. Bag of Zippers always reluctant to close, as if a pull up, I really can't come back.
Pack your bags and leave them by the door
For the first time, I told my parents I loved them on Wechat and didn't dare to tell them the truth. In fact, I am now so afraid of video-chatting with them that I have to act like it doesn't matter, or find a way to amuse them.
I said "I love you" to my parents for the first time

Group in the afternoon deep-fried Pot, the community about 8 pm Chorus, careful owners worried about the spread of flying foam, remind everyone singing on the balcony to wear a mask. I'm a little excited. Before it was time, the person opposite started yelling, "come and Sing at 8 pm! "
When "I and my Motherland" the song resounds in the entire community, when "Wuhan refuels" The cry resounds in the clouds, at that time we, then excited so proud. After a while, some people on Weibo started saying that we were ignorant and could spread saliva by singing on the balcony. We wore masks and said that there weren't enough masks in hospitals and that it was a waste to wear masks at home. We're having a hard time.
I'm going to sleep again, and when I wake up tomorrow morning, I don't know what kind of news will be waiting for me... but I can go back to sleep again, where we hold hands and look for food in the alleys of Wuhan, where we sing side by side in the streets of Wuhan, where we dream, my parents were right there.

January 28,2020
Day Six

January 28,2020

Day Six

Last night dreamed of cold memory of the sauce duck, as well as their chicken feet, woke up in the morning, actually salivated.
The Sun is Shining in Wuhan today. I sat on the balcony in the sun listening to the song, this cozy, not owned for a long time, although the sun is still filled with the smell of disinfectant, but at that moment, I actually hope it can be eternal.
The virus is finally attacking my neighborhood. In the morning, several people wearing protective clothing into the next building, the specific is not clear. Later there is news that the property to re-disinfection what, the Community Group and Fried Pot, and I was unusually calm, continue to cut vegetables, Amoy Rice, busy for the midday food. I know. It's GonNa Happen.
A doctor in a Hazmat suit in the neighborhood

Today, busy busy busy busy busy, busy cooking, busy washing, busy cleaning, busy sleep, busy with the mobile phone... as if only busy, not Random Thoughts. My friend asked me about my temperature in the evening. I just remembered that I hadn't taken my temperature all day. I was too busy.
37 degrees, an awkward number, but I remained calm, not measuring it over and over again, as I had done a few days earlier, for a number that would reassure me.
When tidying up, I came across this picture of Wuhan Tong. At the start of 2020, it inexplicably split in two. At that time, friends joke that the New Year has just begun, broken like this, the moral is not good. His mouth opened like a light. Seeing it, I began to feel sad again.
Wuhan Tong, broken in two

The duffel bag was still at the door, and though it had been packed for a long time, it was my considered choice. But I hope it never comes in handy.
Today, I've learned the truth: the Food I cook, it's really not that bad. On the day when the seal is unsealed, we must have a good time too early. We should eat hot noodles with red oil, baked wheat with oil cake, and three kinds of bean skin. We'd better have a bowl of soup and powder to finish, and then we should say, "serve! "
Seriously, it's killing me.

January 29,2020
Day Seven

January 29,2020

Day Seven

Late last night, I learned that a group of seniors, because of COVID-19 pneumonia left. I broke down. I cried a lot in the middle of the night. We are so small in the face of life and death.
Today is 37 degrees again, but, apart from lying down for a long time a little backache, nothing special feeling. I always feel that there is something wrong with the thermometer at home, and I feel a little nervous when I take my temperature every day. I always feel that this kind of thermometer clip is also wrong, and that kind of clip is also uncomfortable. Sometimes it takes a long time to realize that I have forgotten to look at the time. However, I am glad to see that it has been mixed up, still Healthy.
A daily thermometer

I don't know when, parents began to call me "baby" in Wechat. Before, we always have something to say, will not have such and such call, but now "baby wake up? " "Baby Eat? " Every greeting, will add these two words.
Mom and dad started calling me "baby. "
My parents, like me, were never very good at expressing their feelings. That's an accidental call. They, too, are afraid of something. I was complaining about how hard it was to fake a video with mom and dad, when, in fact, they were all the same. My mother always complained that if only I had lived in Wuhan for a few more months, then I would not be left alone in the face. But, for me, it's a blessing that she's gone.

Recently, too many tears, chat will cry, write a diary will cry, read the news will cry, read Weibo will cry, listen to music will cry... feel like a disaster film, and I, is one of the extras.
Director, don't fall asleep. It's time to say "cut. ".

January 30,2020
Day Eight

January 30,2020

Day Eight

The eighth day, still feel in a dream, everything is so unreal, but this dream is really too long.
Today in Wuhan, the sun is still shining, the upstairs children with his mother in a temper, "let me out, let me out, " hysteria, each cry, as if all the strength is exhausted. I also want to go out for a walk, but looked at the math problem sent by a friend, think or not, the cost of going out is too high.
A few days ago a fever friend, finally broke the fever, she said, she dreamed of eating a bowl of hot dry noodles, wake up, everything will be fine. Authentic Wuhan people, for the hot and dry side of the obsession is really deep.
